description: Just Listed! 470 East 6th St, South Boston - a beautifully maintained multi-family home offering two stylish units in a prime location! The first unit features 2 bedrooms/1 bathroom, while the second unit offers 1 bedroom/1 bathroom. Perfect for investors, owner-occupants, or those seeking rental income. Both units boast gleaming hardwood floors, updated kitchens with modern finishes, and renovated bathrooms. Nestled just blocks from the beach, restaurants & bars, and public transportation, this property combines comfort, convenience, and strong rental potential. Don’t miss this rare opportunity in one of South Boston’s most desirable neighborhoods!
